{
"#name"
:
{
"cron"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"Cron 定时任务管理"
,
"en"
:
"Cron job scheduler"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x cron <subcmd> [options]"
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"轻量级 Cron 定时任务管理模块，支持添加、删除、列表、匹配测试。\n通过命名空间隔离任务，支持按命名空间设定时区。\n支持标准 cron 时间格式（分钟 小时 日 月 星期）。\n每个任务以目录形式存储，包含 cron 表达式、cmd 命令及可选 desc 描述。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Lightweight cron job scheduler with add, remove, list, and match testing.\nJobs are isolated by namespace with per-namespace timezone support.\nSupports standard cron time format (min hour day month dow).\nEach job is stored as a directory containing the cron pattern, cmd script,\nand optional description.\n"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x cron add --name myjob --desc \"say hello\" \"*/5 * * * *\" \"echo hello\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 添加一个每5分钟执行的带描述任务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Add a described job that runs every 5 minutes"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x cron add --once --name greeting \"0 9 * * *\" \"echo good morning\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 添加一个只执行一次的定时任务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Add a one-time job"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x cron ls"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 列出所有任务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: List all jobs"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x cron rm myjob"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 删除任务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Remove a job"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x cron match \"*/5 * * * *\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 测试当前时间是否匹配 cron 表达式"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Test if current time matches a cron pattern"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x cron match \"*/5 * * * *\" \"30 8 16 4 4\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 测试指定时间是否匹配 cron 表达式"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Test if a specific time matches a cron pattern"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x cron tz Asia/Shanghai"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 设置当前命名空间的时区"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Set timezone for current namespace"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x cron service start"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动 cron 守护进程"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start the cron daemon"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x cron run --ns mynamespace"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 前台调试指定命名空间的守护进程"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Debug daemon for a namespace in foreground"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x cron runonce"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 手动触发一次任务补跑"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Manually trigger a one-time job run"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x cron exec myjob"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 直接执行指定任务测试效果"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Execute a specific job directly for testing"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:Job"
:
[
"add"
,
"rm"
,
"ls|list"
,
"match"
]
,
"#subcmd:Run"
:
[
"run"
,
"runonce"
,
"exec"
]
,
"#subcmd:Config"
:
[
"tz"
]
,
"#subcmd:Service"
:
[
"service"
]
,
"#subcmd:Other"
:
[
"--help|-h"
]
,
"add"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"添加一个 cron 任务"
,
"en"
:
"Add a cron job"
}
,
